    "description": "ABOUT THE GAME:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Medieval fantasy single-player game;<br></li><li>Simple and straightforward real-time combat;<br></li><li>10 playable characters available;<br></li><li>World Map with various stages and exploration;<br></li><li>Steam Achievements;<br></li><li>Find treasures that will aid your journey;<br></li><li>Acquire new equipment/weapons/hearts to become stronger;<br></li><li>Solve small puzzles;<br></li><li>Defeat challenging bosses;<br></li><li>Discover the epic story of Eternal Link!</li></ul><br>Indie game developed by one person.<br><br>ATTENTION! By default, the game is in Brazilian Portuguese; on the title screen, go to options to change the language you wish to play in.<br><br>Enjoy the game!<br><br>(C) REFMAP / Degica, Co. LTD<br>(C) Bittersweet Entertainment / Degica, Co. LTD<br><br>=====================================<br><br>In a kingdom on the brink of extinction, the 10 Horsemen of the Apocalypse emerge as the last guardians of hope, summoned by a desperate king. Helping the king free a fearless fairy is just the beginning of an epic tale! Players will be immersed in a saga of mysterious magic, lands to explore, overwhelming challenges, and dramas that thunder in the hearts of the brave. Ready to lead a member of the Horsemen of the Apocalypse and embark on this overwhelming grand journey?<br><br>=====================================",
